{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a96c2764e8","title":"陈伯达对水产部的指示","origin":"1967年11月23日清华大学井冈山斗批改战团编印《学习资料》第50期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5032bf6956","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":21,"articleId":"a96c2764e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3dc6269611","type":"title","text":"陈伯达对水产部的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"e0b281fdcd","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"133ffced62","type":"appellation","text":"〖北京卫戍区谭付参谋长十月二十一日十一时传达〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"51768ddb55","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志于本月十四日对高文华同志的安全问题，有明确指示，要保证高文华的人身安全。为此，我们提出如下要求：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"88864d1f59","type":"paragraph","text":"1．水产部两派群众组织，应遵照伯达同志的指示，要保证高文华同志的人身安全。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"ecdf806217","type":"paragraph","text":"2．水产部两派群众组织，保证高文华同志回机关后的工作方便。不得以任何借口限制他的人身自由。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"f5962593d4","type":"paragraph","text":"3．对上述要求两派群众组织负责人，保证传达各自群众组织的所有成员，人人有责，共同遵守。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"},{"id":"6983a0a955","type":"appellation","text":"（北京卫戍区电话指示）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8"}],"page":{"id":"8c81a123cf","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a96c2764e8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}